title: Origen
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Corner coffee bar and cafe with a pleasant, trendy atmosphere. Uses organic produce and has tofu, veggies, and rice wok dishes. Generally offers 2 mid-day choices of one is vegetarian and sometimes vegan. Has Wi-Fi.
